Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}華盛頓特區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看  腰果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look at that, Cashew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人不聽話了喲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Someone's being a bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}新約聖經  以弗所書  第四章
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"並且不要叫神的聖靈憂愁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Do not grieve the Holy Spirit of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們原是受了他的印記  等候得贖的日子來到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by whom you were sealed for the day of redemption.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切苦毒  惱恨  忿怒  喧嚷  毀謗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let all bitterness and wrath and anger and clamour,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同一切的惡毒  都要從你們中間除掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and evil speaking be put away from you with all malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們要以恩慈相待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And be kind to one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:00:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心存慈憐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}tenderhearted,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此饒恕"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}forgiving one another."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要我繼續讀嗎  還是換一本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want me to keep going with this, or something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.65,0:01:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是喜歡聽你讀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just like hearing you read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  我要跟你說件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug, there's something I need to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.05,0:01:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說她只待幾個晚上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said that she was just staying for a few nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她室友把她趕出來了  她沒地方可以去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her roommate kicked her out. She doesn't have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.93,0:01:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not our problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總不能把她扔到大街上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't put her out on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-麗薩    -姓什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Lisa.   - Lisa what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒什麼好擔心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在在哪裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is she now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:01:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在友誼會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和託兒所的一些小孩一起過夜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a sleepover with some of the kids from the day care.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does she know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我什麼都沒告訴她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I haven't told her anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給了你空間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have given you space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你  瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I trusted you, Rachel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你卻利用...    -我不會把她趕出去的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- and you've taken advantage--   - I'm not kicking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}弗·安德伍德  速來白宮  中國出現危機
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本可以什麼都不說  但我告訴了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could have said nothing, but I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我們再說話前  她最好走人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She better be gone by the next time we talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼久才來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我五分鐘內就能整理好基本情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can have a briefing ready in five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我讓賽斯去做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't bother. I had Seth do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒有安全許可\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't have security clearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he does now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:02:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  你先\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我辦公室等我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll see you in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本主權是最重要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Japanese sovereignty is a matter of precedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首相先生  我的憂慮越來越深了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Prime Minister, my concern is escalation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}隸屬美國太平洋司令部的太平洋艦隊  司令部設在日本的橫須賀港
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只需要第七艦隊的一小部分\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm asking for a small portion of the 7th Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須讓中國認清局面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We must bring China into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向中國展示  日美聯盟堅不可破\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Show them that the U.S. and Japan maintain a strong alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你直接和北京方面聯繫過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you reached out directly to Beijing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們拒不承認該島屬於日本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No recognition that the island belongs to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得和我的團隊討論一下  擬訂一個計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I'd like to speak to my team and formulate a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  首相先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.92,0:03:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上將  給後入會的解釋一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Admiral, for those catching up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.26,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概六小時前  兩艘中國驅逐艦進入了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two Chinese destroyers entered waters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與那國島附近方圓三英里的水域\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}within three miles of Yonaguni Island here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}approximately six hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以看到該島離臺灣很近\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See how close the island is to Taiwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與釣魚島的僵局性質不同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is different than the standoff over the Senkaku Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為航線的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It could have to do with shipping routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者貿易戰  柿子總是撿軟的捏\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or the trade war. They can't pick on the big kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們對實力較弱的下手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so they're picking on the little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看到了嗎    -什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Do you see that?   - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小巷裡  二號機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the alley, camera two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體注意  白人男子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All posts, white male,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帽衫  帆布袋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}hooded sweatshirt, duffel bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法爾大街東南側\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Southeast side of Fair St.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下包\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put down the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放下包  把手放在頭上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put down the bag and place your hands on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住別動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stay right where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你下樓來嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Will you come downstairs, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's Francis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在白宮耽擱了  有個緊急會議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He got delayed at the White House, there was an emergency meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在安全屋做解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll explain in the safe room.
