Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七艦隊在關島附近嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The 7th Fleet is near Guam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北面90英里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ninety miles north.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一週內就能派艦只去與那國島\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We could have ships to Yonaguni in less than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但僅僅向是那個方向行進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But even sending them in that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會被中國衛星發現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will be picked up by the Chinese satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須和盟友保持統一戰線  這毋庸置疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we have to stand with our allies, that can't be in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們不派遣艦隻  而是發表聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if we don't send ships, just make a strong statement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強烈譴責中國擅入日本領海\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}condemning their excursion into Japan's territorial waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得給中國足夠的壓力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We still have to offer the Chinese an incentive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們召回驅逐艦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to call back their destroyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不論採取什麼措施\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever overtures we make,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做好應變計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to have contingency plans in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:06:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經在起草  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Already drafting them, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凱茜  通過外交途徑聯繫北京方面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cathy, open up a diplomatic channel with Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看是否有具體要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See if there's a concrete ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有  就提供一些選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if they don't have one, let's create a list of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就去辦  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同日本海軍的協調如何了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How about coordination with the Japanese navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  暫時不要把我方海軍牽扯進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go. Don't engage with our navy yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要直接和御城首相對話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to talk directly to Prime Minister Oshiro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表達我們的意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and express our intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前海軍陸戰隊員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Former marine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他出現在警戒線附近  拿著一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He showed up at the outer perimeter with explosives
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝滿爆炸物的包  身上也綁著炸藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in a duffel bag and strapped to his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們逮捕了他  媒體沒得到風聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We apprehended him. The press isn't aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  別走漏風聲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, let's keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他宣稱對寄去國會大廈的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He claimed he was responsible for sending
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝有白色粉末的郵件負責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the package of white powder to the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這回他打算對我動真格的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So this time he really wanted to take me out for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能算是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妻子上週揹著他墮胎了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His wife got an abortion last week without telling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天吶  是針對我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, my god. It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  你是目標\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you were the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你和我們留在樓下  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'd like to keep you down here with us, Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們確定他是單獨行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}until we can confirm he was acting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留下陪你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你得回白宮去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. You have to get back to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以在家辦公\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can work from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  我沒事  真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis, I'm fine. Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就待在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna be in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要時刻陪著她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to stick with her at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何事都通知我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep me informed of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他馬上就下班了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's almost done with his shift, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以安排別的探員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can put another agent on--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我就要密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I want it to be Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我待多久我就待多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As long as necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儘快回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back as soon as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去加州\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't go to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想連任呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Be nice to be reelected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會贏的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're gonna win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不在選民前露面就不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if I don't give the voters more face time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候紋的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在軍隊的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之後又添了些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's grown since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我說說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我說說這個紋身\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me about the tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不公平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得讓我溼了我就什麼都會說嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think you can just get me wet and I'll spill everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...I know so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.55,0:10:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡那種疼痛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,針扎的疼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of the needle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多疼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How bad did it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常疼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It hurt a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡疼痛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You like when it hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我殺過很多人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I killed a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在軍隊的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我有幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...it helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.77,0:11:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能找到他開第一家工廠時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The most I could find was some wrangling with the EPA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和環保局的一些爭端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when he opened his first plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那都是40年前了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but that was almost 40 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要更多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.74,0:11:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要塔斯克消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want Tusk gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和道爾會繼續查的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doyle and I will keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還什麼都沒找到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you haven't found anything now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道你能找到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what makes you think you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們忽略了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe we missed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒有  但可以再試試\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I doubt it, but we could try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為塔斯克此刻不是在謀劃下一波進攻嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think Tusk isn't planning his next attack even as we speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們查得很徹底  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've been thorough, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他從來不留痕跡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't leave footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要改變策略嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to shift tactics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那賭場  我們儘快曝光\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The casino. We go public as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說那是萬不得已的辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said that was a last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  想個辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth, you need to find a way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曝光賭場  又不會扯上我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to make that happen so it doesn't link back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們點了這把火\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we launch that missile,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能會燒到我們自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it could blow us up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們控制好就不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if we spin it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-如果我們集中在...    -賽斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- If we keep the focus on--   - Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是來聽的  不是來出謀劃策的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're here to listen, not contribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不想他出謀劃策就不會讓他來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't have him here if I didn't want him to contribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  他接手才三小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir... he's been sitting with this for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經研究了三個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been working on it for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而什麼都沒實現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And accomplished nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該進攻了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's time we go on the offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉·薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ayla Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經在查塔斯克和馮了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's already digging into Tusk and Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她知道多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How close is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她從沒提過賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She never mentioned a casino,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我知道要害在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but now that I know what the dots are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以讓她把一切聯繫起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can see that she's starting to connect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五角大樓還沒有發言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Pentagon isn't talking yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他們在等白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I imagine they're waiting on the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說從昨晚起他們就在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hear there have been regular meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰況室頻繁開會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in the Situation Room since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我過會兒打給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me call you right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好    -你好琳恩  我是艾拉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Hello?   - Hey, Lynne, it's Ayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛發給你張照片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just sent you a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點奇怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.09,0:13:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不太通啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it doesn't really make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字面翻譯應該是"追隨貨幣"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Pursue currency" would be like the most literal translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者"追隨金錢"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Or "pursue money."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Follow the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說也行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  琳恩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks, Lynne.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你的新佈置\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I like what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙發是新的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This sofa, it's new?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這些燈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These lamps as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了些改動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've made a few changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太熟悉一個地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You get so used to a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再小的改變也會很顯眼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the smallest things stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我沒能更快答覆你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I apologize for not being responsive sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近都在忙中期選舉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been focused on the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不用向我解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, there's no need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我多麼尊敬你的初衷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you know how much I respect your intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我經過深思熟慮  還是認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I've thought deeply about this and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能聯署現在這份法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't cosponsor the bill in its current form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民事監管的提議太過極端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Civilian oversight is too extreme a step,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我願意重新考慮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'd be happy to revisit some of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不那麼極端的提議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the other less extreme proposals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我們太極端嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think we're being extremist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想在這件事上出力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to help with this issue,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這份法案要經過...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but this bill goes through--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這份法案要通過三軍委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This bill is through Armed Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入辯論指日可待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This bill has a date on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎眾議院所有的女性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Almost every woman in the House
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都支援這份法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}supports this bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我不能成為其中之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I can't be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙了我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們重新考慮部分措辭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As long as we rethink some of the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是因為嘉樂威醜聞的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you trying to distance yourself from us
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刻意和我們保持距離\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because of the Galloway scandal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許你認為和我合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe you think it hurts your chances
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會對你謀求連任不利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of reelection if you associate with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我打心眼裡不贊同這種方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's because I honestly don't believe in this approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你意識到這會讓外人怎麼看嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you realize the message this sends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是國會兩黨唯一一位女性領導人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only woman in congressional leadership in both parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你選擇退出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you bow out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果法案真能進入辯論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the bill goes to the floor as is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會單單退出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14} I won't just bow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會積極反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll actively fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從未問過我的立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You never asked my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是假設\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You assumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真無法相信你會是什麼立場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine what that position must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾在戰區服役\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've served in war zones,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這事的重要性有親身體會...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know firsthand how important--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在談的不是戰區\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not talking about war zones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是性侵犯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're talking about sexual assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果讓特別軍事法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How about a military commission
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,審查內部機制呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to review the internal mechanisms --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要更多研究  我們需要改革\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't need more studies. We need reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我從加利福尼亞回來以後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, let's continue this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再繼續今天的對話吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when I return from California.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我後天回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back the day after tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但願你會改變想法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望你會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I hope you change yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國認為我們覺得可以收買他們是種侮辱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}China was insulted at the notion we could buy them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我再聯繫錢主席嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, do I need to call President Qian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看他不會與他的部長意見相左\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I doubt he would contradict one of his ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他是否願意一對一談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See if he's willing to talk one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得知道  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should know, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本也正準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Japan is also preparing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調遣三艘驅逐艦和一艘輕巡洋艦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to deploy three destroyers and a light cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在加大賭注\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're upping the ante.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓海因斯大使聯絡日本首相\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have Ambassador Hines get in touch with the prime minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看日本能否暫時按兵不動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and ask if Japan will hold off
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我先和北京取得聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}until I make contact with Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你休息過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you gotten any rest at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒  你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特勤局認為是孤立事件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Secret Service thinks it's an isolated attempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們加強了防備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but they're being cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經過嘉樂威的事和電視採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After the Galloway thing and the interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半數國民當她是嬰兒殺手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}half the country thinks she's a baby killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或出軌者  或兩者皆是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or an adulterer, or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但克萊爾挺坦然的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Claire's taking it in stride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're in good hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可怕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's very frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得你無暇休息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can see why you haven't slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有一人得休息會兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of us should,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是做決策的那個休息吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}probably the one that's calling all the shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  我可以再堅持一會兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I can hold out a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別  回宅邸吧  去陪陪你妻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, go to the residence, spend some time with your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來後會感覺煥然新生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll come back feeling like a new man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Honestly, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的壓力反而更小\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}less stressful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,諮詢沒效果嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Counseling hasn't helped?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  慢慢在起效吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it has... slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達辭職的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got rid of Christina
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也開除了克里斯蒂娜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when Linda resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況多少改善了一些  但是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's improved things some, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需要努力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...there's still work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是想想都讓我覺得累\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Makes me tired just to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該不是第一位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you probably wouldn't be the first president
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這幾個沙發上打盹的總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to get a little shut-eye on one of these sofas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在開玩笑呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.66,0:17:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行行好  休息一下吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do the free world a favor and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先出去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  待在這兒吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, stick around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果錢主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should be nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打電話來  你也該在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if President Qian wants to get on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向討厭睡眠的必要性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've always loathed the necessity of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它跟死亡一樣  能讓最強大的人倒下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like death, it puts even the most powerful men on their backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特區豪車巴士租賃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}DC Limo and Bus Rental.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是阿道希賭場的出行部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm calling from the Adohi Casino's travel department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有公司賬戶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got a corporate account.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我們記錄裡沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I'm sorry, we don't have one in our records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的錯  我一定是打錯電話了  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My mistake. I must have called the wrong limo service. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密蘇里巴士豪車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Missouri Bus and Limo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是阿道希賭場的出行部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm calling from the Adohi Casino's travel department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是達林\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're not Darlene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  達林請病假了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Darlene is out sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我代班  我叫帕姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm filling in for her. My name is Pam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能為你做什麼  帕姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How can I help you, Pam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天要接待來自中國的航班\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've got a flight coming in from China tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll need some transportation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多少乘客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many you got coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我手裡沒有乘客名單\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't have the manifest right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照常嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是一輛豪華巴士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So a luxury bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能坐多少人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many does that fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,55人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}55.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通常拉20個人左右\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Usually about 20 come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-空間應該足夠了    -太棒了  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Should be plenty of room.   - That's great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她是真心不認同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think it's really her conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為法案太有爭議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or because the bill is controversial?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她只是想避免爭議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think she would have threatened to fight us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會說要積極反對了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if all she wanted to do was avoid controversy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟她談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很希望這個法案能通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I really want this bill to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you do, so do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在非常需要傑姬  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need Jackie more than ever, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在成壞女人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm damaged goods,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為亞當那事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}this whole Adam thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起挺過去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We fought past that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是有很多人相信那確有其事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there's plenty of people who still believe it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.72,0:19:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會度過這一關的  我發誓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll get it passed, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己抽沒意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's no fun doing it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.36,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以去跑跑步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We could just go for a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡威脅平息前  不能再去跑步了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No more runs until the death threats die down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是新規則\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's the new rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們讓你去辦公室了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But they let you go to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我坐的是防彈車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I was in a bulletproof car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣一來我們是沒戒菸了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does this mean we've officially not quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們向來不會輕言放棄  不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've never been quitters, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  安德伍德夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, Mrs. Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打擾你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回家了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was gonna head home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你們想讓我留下  我就留下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'll stick around if you want me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你已經熬很久了  去睡會兒吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. You've been up long enough. Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天一早就回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你今天照顧我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for looking after me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的榮幸  女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My pleasure, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  安德伍德夫人  再見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他非常盡忠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's very dedicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.13,0:20:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很難找到艾德華這樣的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's rare to find someone like Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從沒直呼他名字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You never use his first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這樣談論她不太好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't feel right talking about her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是...嚴格講  她現在是我上司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's just... technically, she's my boss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有規矩的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a certain protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是道格下的命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is coming directly from Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說是副總統下的命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which means it's coming directly from the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我見到過幾次丹頓先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have seen Mr. Danton around from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他跟議員女士在商討什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know what he and the congresswoman were discussing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  都是私人會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, they were private meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有預約日程表嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you have the appointment schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看日期\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to look at the dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是正式約會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These weren't formal appointments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是順路來看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He just stops by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多數都是晚上很晚的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most of the time pretty late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,100)}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}沃克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,100)}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}馮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塔斯克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,200)}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}安德伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,200)}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}拉尼根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢是不是從中國來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did the money originate in China?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢來自部落收入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The money came from tribal revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的聯邦選舉委員會報告上寫得很清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As our FEC reports clearly stated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我換個說法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me rephrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些部落收入是否來自\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did any of that revenue come from
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你賭場的中國遊客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Chinese visitors who gambled at your casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有來自世界各地的遊客\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have visitors from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只關注\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm speaking specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫馮山德的商人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about a businessman named Xander Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道那是誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no idea who that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查到空管局的記錄顯示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm looking at FAA flight records that show
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他名下的一架私人飛機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a private plane he owns
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾多次飛抵堪薩斯城\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}making numerous trips to Kansas City.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我問過密蘇里巴士豪車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I spoke with Missouri Bus and Limo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們負責把中國遊客接到你的賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which has transported Chinese visitors to your casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽義德女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Said--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.73,0:21:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:22:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薩伊德女士  我回你的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ms. Sayyad, the only reason I returned your call
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為你在《電訊報》工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}was because you work for The Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是每天都能接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not every day that I get a call
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們這種大報的採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from a paper as big as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不明白你究竟想問什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I don't know what you're trying to get at here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你不介意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so if you'll excuse--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那雷蒙德·塔斯克呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.27,0:22:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮和塔斯克有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng has ties to Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克與總統有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk has ties to the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你與馮有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have ties to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.67,0:22:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這看起來像是外國資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That looks like foreign money
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被用來左右政治...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}being used to influence political--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所暗示的事不僅錯誤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you're insinuating is not only wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是誹謗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's libelous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真實就不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會毫不猶豫地讓我的律師介入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't bat an eyelash getting my attorneys involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克也這麼威脅我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk made the same threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果一個身家四百億的人嚇不倒我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If a man worth $40 billion doesn't intimidate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也嚇不倒我  拉...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you certainly don't, Mr. Lan--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他掛斷了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和這完全沒關係  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with it, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.45,0:22:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在電話這頭都聞得到謊言的臭氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can smell the horseshit through the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我會冒這麼大的險嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think I'd put myself at this great a risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兔子急了都咬人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Desperate men are capable of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣希望事情平息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want it to go away just like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:22:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓她停手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then pull her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我控制不了媒體  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no control over the press, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是搬起石頭砸自己的腳  不是我的  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll destroy yourself, Frank, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你多餘的忠告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for that unsolicited advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和道爾一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Work with Doyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.50,0:23:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確保我們沒有弱點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}make sure we have no weak spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就打電話給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南茜怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did Nancy say?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來傑姬可能和敵人上床了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it looks like Jackie may be sleeping with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根說我們有誹謗的風險沒說錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lanagin is correct in saying we run the risk of libel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們之間的聯繫是有事實依據的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These links are supported by fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是單線  你不能連成圈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Individually, but you can't complete the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說我們要大標題寫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not saying the headline should read:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"洗錢黑幕揭祕"  加大驚歎號\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Money Laundering Scheme Exposed! Exclamation point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是把我們已知的情況原樣呈現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just that we present the landscape as we currently know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們主要是一家財經報紙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're first and foremost a financial paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.15,0:23:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多讀者都崇拜雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Many of our readers worship Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.02,0:23:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就該保護他嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we just protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能暗示我們無法證實的聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't insinuate connections we can't back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.82,0:23:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有任何訴訟的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If there's any basis for litigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的團隊肯定不會放過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you can be sure his team will be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們以前也曾讓報社破產\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They've bankrupted papers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.93,0:23:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該慢慢來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you should slow down and take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候你有了完整的故事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When, and if, you have a story--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克斯菲爾德先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Maxfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德·塔斯克打電話過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk is on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.17,0:23:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他打電話了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you put in a call to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.49,0:23:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他指名要找你  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's specifically asking for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和拉尼根通話還不到半小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We got off the phone with Lanagin less than 30 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明拉尼根立刻打電話給塔斯克了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That means that Tusk was the first call Lanagin made.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他我會打回去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell him I'll return.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聯繫過白宮了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you reach out to the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.61,0:24:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在明天總統的新聞釋出會前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not talking to anyone until after the president
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.61,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不接受任何採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}does his press briefing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把事情再詳細給我說一遍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Walk me through all of this again, point by point.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}華爾街電訊報  中國資金  阿道希賭場
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}沒有搜索到相關網頁
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.44,0:25:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明天再說  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can talk tomorrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.99,0:25:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.17,0:25:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想申請全職做你妻子的安保人員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to put in a request to be on your wife's detail full-time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.09,0:25:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到死亡威脅消失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At least until the death threats quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這很體貼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's very thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.65,0:25:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不同意我是不會去的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll only do it if you approve, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.54,0:25:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和克萊爾談過了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you spoken to Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.69,0:25:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她回來的時候說過了  她覺得不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When she came home. She likes the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.10,0:25:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣做吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I think we should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.81,0:25:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴洛克蘭探員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let Agent Rockland know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打擾  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sorry for interrupting you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.55,0:25:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒打擾什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't interrupt anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.57,0:25:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good night, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.61,0:25:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good night, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.06,0:25:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定猜不到剛才發生了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll never believe what just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.42,0:25:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.02,0:25:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆走進辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum came into the office
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.52,0:25:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現我看的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and found me watching something...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.13,0:25:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是新聞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...other than the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.87,0:26:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.56,0:26:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很懂規矩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was very professional about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.74,0:26:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有沒有...    -沒有  我只是看而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Were you...?   - No, no, no. I was just watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.63,0:26:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好笑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.44,0:26:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢  你在看什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about you? What are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.46,0:26:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康納給我的視訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The video Connor gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們第一次競選州參議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's our first state senate race.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.85,0:26:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘乾淨了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.26,0:26:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  今早在桌上看到才想起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So did I, until I found it in the desk this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.74,0:26:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...經歷過  就像我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...been there, like I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.58,0:26:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  有點德州味兒無傷大雅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course, it doesn't hurt to have a little Texas in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.17,0:26:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-老天  我們當年多年輕    -是啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- My God, look how young we are.   - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.67,0:26:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很和善  很熱情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone here has been so kind, and so welcoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.51,0:26:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過不了多久她就要在克萊姆森紮根了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll have her rooting for Clemson before too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.14,0:26:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我可做不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's where I have to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.84,0:26:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懷念和亞當在一起的日子嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you miss being with Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.31,0:26:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼提起這個來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.33,0:26:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷念嗎  不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Miss it? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.13,0:26:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定偶爾會懷唸的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you must, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.67,0:27:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有段時間很在乎他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He meant a lot to me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.61,0:27:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但都是過去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that's done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.12,0:27:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.06,0:27:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得不滿足嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you unsatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在要時時處處小心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's just too much at stake now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒法信任任何人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one we can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.84,0:27:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了曾經的自由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't have the freedom we once did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.50,0:27:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許這樣更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe it's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.49,0:27:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會分心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No room for distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.95,0:27:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意犧牲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't mind the sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.67,0:27:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們選擇了這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We chose this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.35,0:27:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我們可以達成一致  這兒的肋排更好吃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think the one thing we can agree on is the ribs here are better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.51,0:27:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是不把我惹火不罷休\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See, he's just trying to get under my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.44,0:27:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  根本無可爭辯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it's not even debatable...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.30,0:27:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加州之行怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How was California?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.33,0:28:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很累\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.97,0:28:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩天裡12個活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}12 events in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是金門嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this the Golden Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.21,0:28:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.24,0:28:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我原來在那裡掛了幅未建成的國會大廈蝕刻板畫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had an etching right there of the Capitol before it was finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.02,0:28:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花了85年才完工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Took 85 years to complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.62,0:28:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座橋建了多久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How long did it take to complete the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.50,0:28:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概四年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, about four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.21,0:28:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯福第二次就職演說後不久通行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It opened a few months after FDR's second inaugural.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.80,0:28:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅斯福是個能成事的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was a man who got things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信仰堅定  從不動搖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Strong beliefs. and he stuck to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.55,0:28:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在必要時也會妥協\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But compromised when he had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.40,0:28:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你是來討論克萊爾的法案的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I assume you're here to talk about Claire's bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.01,0:28:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是什麼鬧著玩的項目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not a pet project.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.27,0:28:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩黨加起來有三四十個聯署人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are three dozen cosponsors on either side of the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.27,0:28:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這是個嚴肅的法案    -我不這麼認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- It's a serious bill.   - I don't disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.83,0:28:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,措辭可能稍顯隨意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except with the language.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.55,0:28:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以解釋我的看法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can explain my thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.93,0:28:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但恐怕不能說服你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I doubt I'll convince you anymore--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.76,0:28:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不提什麼軍隊尊嚴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Putting aside the military's honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.18,0:28:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍階等級  等等一切你珍視的東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}chain of command, all the things that you hold dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.03,0:28:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就考慮一個簡單的事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...let's consider one simple fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.04,0:29:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我  你坐不進這間辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You wouldn't have this office if it weren't for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.34,0:29:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得很清楚  我不會做傀儡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I made very clear that I wouldn't be a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.99,0:29:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想控制你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not trying to pull strings,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.96,0:29:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你好歹表現出一點感激\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you could show a little gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.67,0:29:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別的都可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it were anything else,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.57,0:29:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.68,0:29:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這件事不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but not this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.55,0:29:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事必然要成功  你至多只會讓好事多磨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you're doing is making the inevitable more difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.58,0:29:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非一定會成功  克萊爾還沒得到足夠的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not inevitable. Claire doesn't have the votes yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.65,0:29:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真想在這件事上和我們對著幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You really want to fight us on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.69,0:29:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點不想和你對著幹\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to fight you at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.86,0:29:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才向克萊爾建議  我們坐下來談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which is why I suggested to Claire that we sit down--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.83,0:29:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我既沒有時間  也沒有興趣和你討價還價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I neither have the time nor the inclination to negotiate with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.40,0:29:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯署法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cosponsor the bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.63,0:29:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉好該死的票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whip the damn votes,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.91,0:29:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是請求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm no longer asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.60,0:29:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不會再聽了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I'm no longer listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.51,0:29:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該謝我的  可不止這間辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have just this office to thank me for.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.53,0:29:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如果能連任  還要為那個謝我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you win reelection, you can thank me for that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.83,0:29:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些攻擊廣告可不是平白無故消失的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those attack ads didn't just disappear on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.10,0:29:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.04,0:29:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去問問雷米·丹頓吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't you ask Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.76,0:29:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,順便再問問他雷蒙德·塔斯克的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And ask him about Raymond Tusk while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.27,0:30:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的枕邊對話會很有意思的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That ought to make for some very interesting pillow talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.97,0:30:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續好好工作  南茜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You keep up the good work, Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.28,0:30:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.79,0:30:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念你在身邊的日子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I miss having you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.42,0:30:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在你是我的眼線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you're my eyes and ears now,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.17,0:30:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則我立馬把你要回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}otherwise I'd steal you back in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.69,0:30:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.43,0:30:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說  對我意義重大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It means a lot to me that you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.45,0:30:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忙著呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.47,0:30:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報道剛剛見報了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The story just broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.15,0:30:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們算準了總統的新聞釋出會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They timed it with the president's press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.66,0:30:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我轉接副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Connect me with the vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.89,0:30:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs16\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}政治行動委員會資金引起質疑  雷蒙德·塔斯克  中國資金  國會和白宮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.11,0:30:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第七艦隊目前部署在關島附近\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So the 7th Fleet is currently positioned near Guam,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.28,0:30:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果中國將船隻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}where it will remain
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.57,0:30:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從日本領海撤出  第七艦隊也會原地不動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if China removes its ships from Japan's sovereign waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和御城首相保持著頻繁的溝通\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been in frequent touch with prime minister Oshiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.71,0:31:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也親自向錢主席發出提議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and have made personal overtures to President Qian.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.33,0:31:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對緩解緊張局勢持樂觀態度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I remain optimistic that tensions will be quelled
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.76,0:31:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危機不會進一步升級\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without any further escalations.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.18,0:31:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我可以回答一些問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, with that, I'll take some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.22,0:31:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亨利  你先來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Henry, you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.28,0:31:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以對《華爾街電訊報》的報道發表評論嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you comment on the Wall Street Telegraph article--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.58,0:31:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來之前才剛知道這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was just notified of that moments before I joined you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.43,0:31:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒來得及看呢  簡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't had a chance to read it yet. Yeah, Jane?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.31,0:31:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.06,0:31:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能給我們講一下你和雷蒙德·塔斯克的關係嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}would you walk us through your history with Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.82,0:31:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是來回答關於中日關係的問題的  馬克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here to answer questions on Sino-Japanese relations. Mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.50,0:31:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報道中提到馮山德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The article mentions Xander Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位富有而有影響力的中國商人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a wealthy and influential Chinese businessman --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.92,0:31:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非問題與我剛剛的聲明有關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless this has to do with the statement I just made...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.21,0:31:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確有關  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It does, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.45,0:31:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮和常委有聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng has ties to the standing committee
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.20,0:31:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們目前和中國陷入僵局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we're currently in a standoff with the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.06,0:31:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,經濟上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Economically--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.64,0:31:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝各位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.08,0:31:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不怕這故事的開端\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not beginning the story that I fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.75,0:31:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕的是不知道結局將如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's not knowing how it will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.19,0:31:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在人人都是靶子了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone is fair game now,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.44,0:31:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.32,0:31:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這完全在意料之中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is par for the course,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.51,0:31:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經發現沃克總統就是如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for what we've come to expect from President Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.72,0:31:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}印第安捐助者  沃克對詳情閃爍其辭
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.70,0:31:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他想賣出一輛新車\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whenever he's selling a shiny new car,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.51,0:31:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就滔滔不絕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he can't say enough about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.00,0:32:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎壞了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The engine breaks down,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.06,0:32:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變速器不好使了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the transmission gives out,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.56,0:32:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就開始閃爍其詞  無視保修\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he dodges, he ignores the warranty.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.74,0:32:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來告訴你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的保修單叫做美國憲法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}our warranty is the constitution of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.08,0:32:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這張保修單是沒有限制條件的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and there's no limit on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.61,0:32:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他得好好看看憲法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He needs to read the fine print
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.13,0:32:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且開始回答我們的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and start answering our questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.60,0:32:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}贓款: 最高涉及到哪一層
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.61,0:32:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這裡確有屬實的內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If any of this is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.88,0:32:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是國會  白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we're talking Congress, the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.41,0:32:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及兩黨都算上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}both parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.32,0:32:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說如果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, I'm saying "If,"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.56,0:32:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果這錢看起來像贓款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but when it looks like dirty money,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.18,0:32:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聞上去也像贓款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and it smells like dirty money,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.61,0:32:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定有人手上沾著髒東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}somebody has probably got dirt under their nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.40,0:32:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有證據表明洗錢活動確實...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, there's no real proof this money laundering is even--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.45,0:32:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可這其中的聯繫令人擔憂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The connections are troubling,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.78,0:32:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}especially Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.19,0:32:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿道希資助民主黨期間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was the House whip the entire time Adohi were
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.23,0:32:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾拉·薩伊德  《華爾街電訊報》
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.32,0:32:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一直是黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}contributing to the Democrats,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.47,0:32:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在他在總統身邊工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and he's working side by side with the president now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.72,0:32:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統  這事能一路牽連到白宮嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president. So this goes all the way to the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.85,0:32:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這只是假設\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's hypothetical.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.38,0:32:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  你為了證實說法  證據都是挑揀過的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And by the way, you've cherry-picked the facts to make your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.89,0:32:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼說法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not making a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.23,0:32:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的標題是《政治行動委員會資金引起質疑》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My headline is: PAC Money Raises Questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.57,0:32:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也確實有疑問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.92,0:32:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有給出答案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't answered those questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得美國人民應該知道答案  你覺得呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I think the American people deserve answers. Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.85,0:32:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can bet your bottom dollar
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.87,0:32:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百會介入調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the attorney general is gonna investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.97,0:32:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事已經在媒體上引起了軒然大波\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With the firestorm this is causing in the media--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.07,0:32:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's our course of action?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.24,0:33:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為你的法律顧問  我建議你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As your counsel, I would encourage you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.89,0:33:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在有更多訊息之前不要和媒體接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not to speak to the press until we have more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.12,0:33:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為普通公民\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As your average citizen,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.20,0:33:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你等的越久  看起來就越可疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the longer you wait, the more suspicious it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.40,0:33:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有任何的違規行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If there's been any irregularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.68,0:33:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都與我沒有關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.50,0:33:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和塔斯克的友誼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your friendship with Tusk
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.59,0:33:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會讓你因關連而被認為有罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}implies guilt by association.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.71,0:33:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們現在是做有罪推定了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are we presuming guilt before innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.80,0:33:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是個律師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm a lawyer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.75,0:33:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不做任何假設\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I presume nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.53,0:33:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是輿論可沒有法律學位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But public opinion doesn't have a law degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.77,0:33:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們單獨說兩句\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give us a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.72,0:33:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須建議你  如果我不在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to advise you not to have any conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.06,0:33:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要和任何人討論這件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about this matter without me present.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.82,0:33:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解你的建議了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your advisement has been noted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.94,0:33:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在門口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.64,0:33:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你一直沒和我說的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this what you were keeping from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.06,0:33:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該遵照你法律顧問的建議  不應該...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should follow your counsel's advice, and not --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.99,0:33:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我  錢的事是不是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me if it's true, about the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.46,0:33:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比爾不在房間裡  我們可能出現各種...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With Bill out of the room, we open ourselves up to all sort of--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.60,0:33:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死  弗蘭克  這事我已經被瞞得太久了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Damn it, Frank! I've been in the dark too long on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.62,0:33:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That ends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道任何細節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know any details.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.27,0:34:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮說如果大橋的項目通過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng told me if the Bridge project got approved,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.77,0:34:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給共和黨的資金就會斷流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the GOP would stop getting money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.34,0:34:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們批准了項目  資金就停了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We approved it, the money stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.75,0:34:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爺  這樣白宮和錢就有直接聯繫了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jesus Christ, that connects the White House directly to the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不知道  過去是  現在也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You knew nothing, you still know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.94,0:34:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果司法部發現任何確鑿證據證明外來資金...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the DOJ finds any concrete evidence of foreign money--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.57,0:34:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是雷蒙德·塔斯克的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's Raymond Tusk's head,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.91,0:34:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的  你什麼都沒做錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not yours. You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.59,0:34:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牽連罪  弗蘭克  你也聽到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Guilt by association, Frank. You heard the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.69,0:34:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果司法部進行調查  只會證明你是無罪的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the DOJ investigates, it will only prove your innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.92,0:34:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能從這種事情中全身而退\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nobody walks away from something like this without bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.57,0:34:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但傷不致命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, bruises you can survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是不知事到如今要如何避免受牽連\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just don't know how we can avoid it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.41,0:34:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想加快程序  平息此事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless you want to accelerate the process and get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.74,0:34:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以讓司法部長任命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We could always have the attorney general appoint
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.80,0:34:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一名特別檢察官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a special prosecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.65,0:34:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這主意太糟了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.63,0:34:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.60,0:34:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鑑於我們現在的情況  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And given where we are, Frank,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.87,0:34:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很想接受你的建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not inclined to follow your suggestions.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.73,0:34:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說你該這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I wasn't suggesting it as something you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.27,0:34:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是提出一種可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just as a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.42,0:34:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實  我覺得你不該這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, in fact, I --I don't think you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.31,0:34:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這種事拖得越久越好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think it's better to drag these things out as long as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.19,0:34:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓公眾對這個話題產生厭煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let the public fatigue on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.66,0:34:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到中期選舉都一直對我們構成威脅嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And have it hanging over our heads until the midterms?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.74,0:34:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熱度會消退的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It'll lose steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.69,0:34:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有怎麼辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What if it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.95,0:35:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國防部提出要對中國南海發起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've got the Pentagon proposing tactical drone strikes
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.18,0:35:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰術性無人機襲擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in the South China Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.19,0:35:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能好幾個月糾纏在這種事裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't be dealing with something like this for months on end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.52,0:35:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許你說得對  是該任命個特別檢察官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe you're right then. A special prosecutor is the way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.37,0:35:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那麼說  是你說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't say that, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.54,0:35:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是說讓你擺脫這個問題的糾纏\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, no. I just meant in terms of getting it off your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.46,0:35:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你及時彙報情況  我就不會有這個問題了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It wouldn't be on my plate if you kept me better informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.66,0:35:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直是在幫你撇清干係  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have done nothing but try to insulate you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.44,0:35:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛媒體對我的攻擊叫撇清干係嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that what you call the feeding frenzy I just went through?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.88,0:35:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你鄭重承諾  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I make this solemn promise to you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.35,0:35:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果走到那一步  我會承擔罪責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will take the fall if it comes to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.97,0:35:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.71,0:35:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論你打算如何處理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}However you decide to deal with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.55,0:35:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你的直覺是對的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think your instincts are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.79,0:35:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能不該指派特別檢察官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We probably shouldn't involve a special prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.64,0:35:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓比爾回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Send Bill back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.67,0:35:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You knew about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.48,0:35:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克是我的客戶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk is a client,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.27,0:35:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但我不是什麼都知道    -胡說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- doesn't mean I know everything--   - Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.92,0:35:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以能成為格蘭頓-希爾的合夥人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The reason you're a partner at Glendon Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.86,0:35:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你知道內幕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is because you know the things nobody else does.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.18,0:35:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.91,0:35:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.48,0:36:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不談公事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't talk about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒在床上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not in bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.51,0:36:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是在我的辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we're in my fucking office.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.96,0:36:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.07,0:36:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為弗蘭克賣命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you work for Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.17,0:36:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只為我自己賣命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I work for no one but myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.92,0:36:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續自欺欺人吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep telling yourself that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.97,0:36:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像你  我不把自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unlike you, I don't peddle my goods
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.11,0:36:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣給出價最高的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for whoever can pay the highest retainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.78,0:36:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是很多老大的走狗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the bitch to a lot of top dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.57,0:36:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己很清楚也很情願\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fully aware and willing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.35,0:36:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你比我更糟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you're worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.50,0:36:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是弗蘭克的走狗  還拒不相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're Frank's bitch and refuse to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.70,0:36:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.71,0:36:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我戳中了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Case in fucking point.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.88,0:36:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別轉移話題  你知道這筆錢卻沒有告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't turn this. You knew about the money and you didn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.86,0:36:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管這事會動搖我的職位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even though it's thrown my seat into contention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.01,0:36:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算錢的事屬實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's say there was money,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.43,0:36:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也確實知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and let's say I did know,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.13,0:36:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你有什麼好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what good would it have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.94,0:36:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這說明你不惜看著我輸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It means you were willing to watch me lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.21,0:36:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在尊重你提出的界限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It means I respected the boundaries that you demanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.46,0:36:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不改變關係  沒有特殊待遇    -這是兩碼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- No changes, no special treatment.   - This is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.80,0:36:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還要開特例了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So now we're making exceptions?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.16,0:36:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的事情當然算特例\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When it's this important, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.59,0:36:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魚和熊掌不可兼得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't have it both ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.59,0:36:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Were you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.20,0:36:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.01,0:37:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了打探弗蘭克的訊息才上我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...fucking me to get info on Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.62,0:37:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼想嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.34,0:37:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.59,0:37:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你的關心已經太多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I care about you more than I should,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我厭倦了總要一遍遍地說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm getting tired of having to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.65,0:37:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被轉移到一家聯邦精神病院做評估\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's being moved to a federal psychiatric facility for assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.49,0:37:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式判刑前待在高警戒的拘留中心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then a high-security detention center until the official sentencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.63,0:37:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.44,0:37:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壞訊息是  我們希望你近期不要公開活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The bad news is we don't want you doing any public events for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的法案馬上要表決了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My bill is about to go to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.63,0:37:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須公開露面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to have a public profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.52,0:37:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的死亡威脅越來越嚴重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your death threats continue to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.58,0:37:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們冒不起這個險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.06,0:37:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能離開家了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Am I even allowed to leave the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.07,0:37:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以  但我們希望你避開人群\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course. But we want you to avoid large crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.60,0:37:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們保護你的能力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our ability to protect--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.44,0:37:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.08,0:37:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.46,0:37:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是在跟安德伍德夫人彙報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We were just briefing Mrs. Underwood
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.94,0:37:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的新安保規程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on her new security protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.62,0:38:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們待會兒再說行嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we actually finish this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.52,0:38:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.78,0:38:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.94,0:38:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他起了疑心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's skeptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.88,0:38:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我給特莉莎打電話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should I call Tricia?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.84,0:38:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不能讓他覺得我在他背後搗鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It could look like i was trying to go behind his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只需要靜觀其變\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll just have to wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.49,0:38:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的都說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I made my case.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.61,0:38:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他不會同意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hopefully, he'll disagree with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.56,0:38:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這可能是招錯棋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But this could've been the wrong move.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.00,0:38:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要懷疑你自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, don't doubt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.52,0:38:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯在過去六小時裡收到了三千餘封電子郵件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth has gotten over 3,000 e-mails in the last six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.27,0:38:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話被打爆了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The phones are overloaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.77,0:38:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要完全無視嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you ignore all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.01,0:38:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能無視司法部\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't ignore the Department of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.55,0:38:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.20,0:38:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我進監獄了來探視我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come and visit me when I'm in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.42,0:38:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不非得站在門口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to stand by that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.44,0:39:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆會兒吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take a load off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.78,0:39:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生  但我應該站著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir, but I'm supposed to stay on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.90,0:39:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不說我也不說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I won't tell if you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.37,0:39:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人為這個找你麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if anybody gives you any trouble about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.28,0:39:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是為任何事找你麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.22,0:39:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以來找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they can talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.06,0:39:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚真美\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Beautiful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.47,0:39:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.08,0:39:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天你不在身邊的感覺真有點怪呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's been strange not having you around these last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.52,0:39:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我回到你的安保隊伍中嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to switch back to your detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.34,0:39:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你跟克萊爾在一起我很欣慰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no. I'm glad you're with Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.66,0:39:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你走了我才發覺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just didn't realize how much
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.74,0:39:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有多習慣你在我身邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got used to your company until you were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.63,0:39:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中保護她和保護你是一回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Protecting her is the same as protecting you in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.66,0:39:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.16,0:40:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要做這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why do you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.21,0:40:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do what, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.01,0:40:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一直讓我感到敬畏\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've always been awestruck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.76,0:40:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然會有人願意為別人擋子彈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People who are willing to take a bullet for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.29,0:40:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我為國家服務的方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's how I serve my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為國家服務的方式還有很多種\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a lotta ways to serve your country.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.67,0:40:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this is my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.49,0:40:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這瓶我還沒喝完呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I haven't finished with this one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.31,0:40:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是給你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.27,0:40:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我執勤的時候不能喝酒  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't drink on duty, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.20,0:40:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是給你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not for you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.47,0:40:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  過來一起聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, come on over and join the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.03,0:40:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒看膩我的臉嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Haven't you got sick of seeing my face yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.81,0:40:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會  夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.68,0:40:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To Meechum,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.44,0:40:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬他的忠誠與服務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for his loyalty and service.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.28,0:40:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬艾德華\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.81,0:41:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在去我律師辦公室的路上  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on my way to my lawyer's office, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.19,0:41:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平常這時候我已經睡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not where I want to be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.12,0:41:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想去那地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when I'd usually be in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.70,0:41:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法阻止弗蘭克洩露訊息\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't stop Frank from leaking things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.91,0:41:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  但你可以讓他比我們更遭罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, but you can make sure he suffers more than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.18,0:41:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說"我們"  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I say "us," Remy,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.02,0:41:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為現在你也是一條繩上的螞蚱了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because your skin is in this game now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.79,0:41:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你準備否認嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna deny?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.46,0:41:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然要否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course I'm gonna deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.05,0:41:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事每個步驟都是合法的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every step of this was legal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們無法證明其中的聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can't prove the links between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.66,0:41:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根那邊呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What about Lanagin?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.27,0:41:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會合作的  我們要擔心的是馮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'll cooperate. It's Feng we need to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.89,0:41:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想個辦法聯繫他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll find a way to get in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.82,0:41:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有一項優勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We do have one major advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.83,0:41:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公眾可以恨我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The public can hate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.21,0:41:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只要克雷頓-維斯特還在盈利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but as long as Clayton West remains profitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.93,0:41:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的股東們就不會在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my stockholders won't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.14,0:41:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克可不行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank doesn't have the same liberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.90,0:41:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公眾輿論就可以毀了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Public opinion can demolish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.80,0:41:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得確保事態會這樣發展\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to make sure that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.75,0:42:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以跟共和黨人一起想辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can work with the Republicans on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.33,0:42:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會遭人仔細審視\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we'll be under the magnifying glass too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.78,0:42:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會變成一場政治迫害\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This will be a witch hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.03,0:42:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我會讓他們抓到該抓的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure that they pick the right targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.06,0:42:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要攻擊領導層\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you need to do is go after the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.08,0:42:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們受苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make them hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.12,0:42:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會為了自救背叛弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll turn on Frank to save themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.01,0:42:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博奇  烏麥克  夏普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Birch, Womack, Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.05,0:42:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是傑姬·夏普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Especially Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.87,0:42:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是他欽點的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's his chosen one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.91,0:42:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.63,0:42:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽著呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.84,0:42:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這就行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got my marching orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.58,0:42:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就看你的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.74,0:42:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不辱使命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll deliver.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.39,0:42:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明早再談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's talk in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.39,0:42:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最看好的兩個人是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The two names I like the most
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.54,0:42:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賈斯汀·蓋因斯和希瑟·鄧巴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}are Justin Gaines and Heather Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.33,0:42:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋因斯的資歷更高\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Gaines has better credentials.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他跟政府關係太近\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's close to the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.38,0:42:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是共和黨阻撓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would've made him a federal judge
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.66,0:42:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經讓他當上聯邦法官了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if the GOP hadn't blocked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.95,0:42:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點很重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's an important point.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.14,0:42:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴很勇敢  她絕對可以勝任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dunbar's got grit. She's more than qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.20,0:42:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且沒有負擔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And there's no baggage there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.32,0:42:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她更難以捉摸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But she's more unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.27,0:42:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果司法部長認為她是個未知數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I doubt the attorney general would have put her on his list
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.29,0:42:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會把她提上名單了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he thought she was a wild card.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.66,0:42:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我必須說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, I have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.28,0:42:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這一步時機不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think this step is premature.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.42,0:43:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該緩緩  看看司法部自己採取什麼行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should hold off and see what the DOJ does on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.85,0:43:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想這麼做  比爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to do it, Bill
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.89,0:43:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的擔心是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But my fear is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.56,0:43:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們等著水從熱升至沸騰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we wait until the water goes from hot to boiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.64,0:43:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會顯得我們太保守了  缺乏積極性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we seem reactionary, not proactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.54,0:43:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但積極也可能顯得防禦性太強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But proactive could also seem defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.28,0:43:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像嫌疑人在別人問之前就大喊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like the suspect that screams "I didn't do it"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.16,0:43:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我幹的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before anyone asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.24,0:43:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外  我們根本沒時間做準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aside from that, we simply haven't had time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.80,0:43:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許等幾禮拜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe wait a couple of weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.89,0:43:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就達不到目的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That defeats the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.91,0:43:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就等幾天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.68,0:43:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要選鄧巴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to go with Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.80,0:43:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-先生    -我決定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Sir--   - I've made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.24,0:43:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比爾  請你將我的意思轉達給司法部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bill, I'd like you to convey my wishes to the attorney general.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.95,0:43:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是得由他決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ultimately, the decision is his.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.87,0:43:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能給他施加壓力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't appear to be pressuring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.40,0:43:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.89,0:43:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.87,0:43:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一比說服別人按我的意願做事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only thing more satisfying than
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.80,0:43:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更讓我感到滿足的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}convincing someone to do what I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.75,0:43:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是故意沒能說服他們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is failing to persuade them on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.01,0:43:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像"禁止進入"標誌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's like a "Do Not Enter" Sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.49,0:43:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是在求你走進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it just begs you to walk through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.58,0:43:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道爾對我們的初步背景調查已經進行過半了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doyle's about halfway through our initial background check.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.76,0:43:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每位捐贈人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every donor,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.64,0:43:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次政治活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}every political event.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.73,0:43:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴可能調查的每件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything that Dunbar might be looking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.44,0:43:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  賽斯呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good. Seth?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要避免做任何正式聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We avoid any official statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.62,0:43:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽總統的指令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}follow the president's cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.07,0:43:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時  我想打幾個非正式電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, I'd like to make some off the record calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.89,0:44:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透露說你樂於接受調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You welcome the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.05,0:44:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做是對的  等等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's the right step, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.30,0:44:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓民眾瞭解你的個人看法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give folks the personal touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.67,0:44:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  只要不顯得我們防禦性太強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's fine, as long as we don't come off defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.11,0:44:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你要給誰打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to see a list of who you'd be calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.64,0:44:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人可能會很忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Some of this is gonna be on the fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.94,0:44:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能讓我自由發揮會更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it'd be great if I had a little leeway.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.24,0:44:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓賽斯幹他的  道爾的事就夠你忙的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let Seth do his thing, you'll have your hands full with Doyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.63,0:44:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我事後告訴你我都打給誰了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll let you know who I've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.63,0:44:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  工作去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.90,0:44:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.42,0:44:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.91,0:44:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你要委派任務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand that you need to delegate,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.92,0:44:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你當著賽斯的面反駁我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but when you contradict me in front of Seth,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.47,0:44:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會削弱我對他的控制\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it compromises my authority over him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.15,0:44:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能事事管著他  我們要忙的事很多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't micromanage, we have too much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.90,0:44:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯還是我們團隊裡的新人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth is still new to the team.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.72,0:44:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確保他在好好完成任務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to make sure that he's doing his job properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他在好好做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.94,0:44:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的故障保險  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am your failsafe, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你不讓我這麼做  我就沒辦法了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I can't be that if you won't let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.85,0:44:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  道格  你是我的故障保險嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you, Doug? My failsafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.27,0:44:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還懷疑這點嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you doubt that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.91,0:45:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在全速飛向一場颶風\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're flying full throttle into a hurricane,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.14,0:45:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你卻在談辦公室政治\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you're talking office politics
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.97,0:45:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是集中全力確保我們不會被搞垮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}instead of focusing on making sure we don't get ripped apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.73,0:45:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對  先生  我不該提這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're right, sir. I shouldn't have brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.51,0:45:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還在那裡嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.43,0:46:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在  我告訴她我去散個步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I told her I was going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.45,0:46:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  我知道你說過你想讓她走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Doug, I know you said you wanted her gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.98,0:46:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要理解  我只求...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you have to understand that all I'm asking is --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.42,0:46:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可以留下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.33,0:46:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.27,0:46:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不一定得走  她可以留下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She doesn't have to leave. She can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.15,0:46:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你知道分寸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I trust you to be smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.83,0:46:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能讀書給我聽嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Will you read to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.95,0:46:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的《聖經》在屋裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My bible is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.39,0:46:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不非得是《聖經》\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doesn't have to be the bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.71,0:46:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便找點你手機上的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just pull up something on your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.92,0:46:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.36,0:46:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《雙城記》  我媽媽以前會念給我聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tale of Two Cities. My mom used to read it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.32,0:46:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最美好的時代\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was the best of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.62,0:46:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是最糟糕的時代\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the worst of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.32,0:46:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是智慧的年頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the age of wisdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.07,0:47:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是愚昧的年頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the age of foolishness,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.54,0:47:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是信仰的紀元\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the epoch of belief,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.00,0:47:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是懷疑的紀元\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the epoch of incredulity,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.69,0:47:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是光明的季節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the season of Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.63,0:47:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是黑暗的季節\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the season of Darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.60,0:47:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是希望的春天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it was the spring of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.14,0:47:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是絕望的冬天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the winter of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.26,0:47:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們擁有一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we had everything before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.68,0:47:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一無所有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we had nothing before us,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.55,0:47:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都將直奔天堂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we were all going direct to Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.68,0:47:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都將直落地獄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we were all going direct the other way."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.64,0:47:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.13,0:47:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  是你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.46,0:47:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.47,0:47:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.29,0:47:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.65,0:48:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}喬帕  道·斯坦普
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.51,0:48:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  道格  就是你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, Doug, it is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.90,0:48:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(193,145)\fad(500,500)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscy1800\fscx3400\c&H000000&\bord1\shad0}■
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.90,0:48:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(800,800)\fs18\pos(193,145)\fn方正小標宋_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\b1}本集一開始  一個反墮胎者試圖襲擊克萊爾\N美國建國早期\N除了一些法律禁止銷售能夠引起晚期流產的藥物之外\N墮胎行為是被允許的\N自從1821年康涅狄格州第一個通過了禁止墮胎的法律後\N其它各州也紛紛仿效\N聯邦政府也在1883年通過了禁止傳播避孕和墮胎工具\N藥物和資訊的"康斯托克法"\N在1973年1月22日最高法院公佈"羅訴韋德案"判決結果之前\N除非妊娠威脅到孕婦的生命安全  墮胎在美國全境都是非法的
